Cost-effectiveness of capecitabine and bevacizumab maintenance treatment after 
first-line induction treatment in metastatic colorectal cancer.

Franken MD(1), van Rooijen EM(2), May AM(3), Koffijberg H(4), van Tinteren H(5), 
Mol L(6), Ten Tije AJ(7), Creemers GJ(8), van der Velden AMT(9), Tanis BC(10), 
