The status of intensive care medicine research and a future agenda for very old 
patients in the ICU.

Flaatten H(1)(2), de Lange DW(3), Artigas A(4), Bin D(5), Moreno R(6), 
Christensen S(7), Joynt GM(8), Bagshaw SM(9), Sprung CL(10), Benoit D(11), 
